# EthioShop Web Icons
# 
# Place your app icons in this directory.
# 
# Required icons:
# - Icon-192.png (192x192 px)
# - Icon-512.png (512x512 px)
# - Icon-maskable-192.png (192x192 px, for adaptive icons)
# - Icon-maskable-512.png (512x512 px, for adaptive icons)
# 
# You can generate these icons from a single source image using:
# - https://realfavicongenerator.net/
# - https://www.pwabuilder.com/imageGenerator
# - Flutter icon generation tools
#
# For best results:
# - Use a simple, recognizable logo
# - Use your brand colors
# - Ensure good contrast on light and dark backgrounds
# - Test on different devices and browsers